# simple cube

mtllib cube.mtl
o cube
v 0 0 0
v 0 0 1
v 0 1 1
v 0 1 0
v 1 0 0
v 1 0 1
v 1 1 1
v 1 1 0

vn -1  0  0
vn  1  0  0
vn  0 -1  0
vn  0  1  0
vn  0  0  1
vn  0  0 -1

vt 0.0 1.0
vt 1.0 1.0
vt 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 0.0

usemtl Red
f 1//1 2//1 3//1 # left side
f 3//1 4//1 1//1
f 3//4 7//4 4//4 # upper side
f 7//4 8//4 4//4
f 2//5 6//5 7//5 # front side
f 7//5 3//5 2//5
usemtl Textured
f 5/2/2 7/4/2 6/3/2 # right side
f 7/4/2 5/2/2 8/1/2
f 1/1/3 5/2/3 2/4/3 # bottom side
f 5/2/3 6/3/3 2/4/3
f 1/2/6 4/3/6 5/1/6 # back side
f 5/1/6 4/3/6 8/4/6